<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd">
<task id="send_the_student_an_email_notifying_them_that_their_feedback_is_ready">
    <title>Send the student an email notifying them that their feedback is ready. </title>
    <shortdesc></shortdesc>
    <taskbody>
        <context>Send an email notification with our predefined template response. </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Open the email templates by clicking on the second icon from the left menu
                    bar.</cmd>
                <info>
                    <fig id="fig_it3_2fs_jfc">
                        <title><i>Open email templates.</i></title>
                        <image href="images/open_email_templates.png" id="image_jt3_2fs_jfc"/>
                    </fig>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Under the CONTACT NOTIFICATION section click the template named No PDF Feedback
                    Ready to add the templateâ€™s text to the email.</cmd>
                <info>
                    <fig id="fig_ekt_fxr_jfc">
                        <p>
                            <fig id="fig_tlv_kfs_jfc">
                                <title><i>Select the <b>No PDF Feedback Ready</b> option</i></title>
                                <image href="images/select_the_no_pdf_%20feedback_ready_option.png"
                                    id="image_ulv_kfs_jfc"/>
                            </fig>
                        </p>
                    </fig>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>After clicking, it should include a short message that the feedback is ready
                    and a URL to the feedback in our application. Before sending the final response,
                    re-check the following:</cmd>
                <substeps id="substeps_jpn_3xr_jfc">
                    <substep>
                        <cmd>URL includes the site URL and the ticket URL.</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep>
                        <cmd>Site URL can be found in the <b>Additional Information</b> section of
                            the ticket.</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep>
                        <cmd>Upload URL can be found in the <b>Paper</b> section of the ticket. </cmd>
                        <info>
                            <fig id="fig_f24_txr_jfc">
                                <p>
                                    <fig id="fig_rcq_nfs_jfc">
                                        <title><i>Include the site URL</i></title>
                                        <image href="images/include_the_site_url.png"
                                            id="image_scq_nfs_jfc"/>
                                    </fig>
                                </p>
                            </fig>
                        </info>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
